  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb4\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Soon people's expectation will be fulfilled - Dulles beauty",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Had I won the new presidential election held in Parliament, I would have been considered the 8th president with executive powers. There is no place for people's voice and demands in Parliament. Former minister Dalus Alagaperuma said that people's expectations will be fulfilled very soon.",
        "He mentioned the above while attending a press conference in Colombo yesterday.",
        "We voted against it because of the consequences of emergency legislation.",
        "Those who participated in the discussion regarding the emergency law before it was brought to the parliament said that they would vote against the emergency law and others expressed their opposition to the government by not participating in the vote.",
        "Accordingly, five members of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna voted against the Emergency Act, while 33 members of the Podujana Peramuna abstained from voting and expressed their opposition to the government.",
        "The head of state has the responsibility to protect the basic rights of the people of the country. Attempting to block the democratic struggle of the people with power will have opposite effects. Rulers should understand that.",
        "We worked dedicatedly for the victory of Podujana Peramuna's candidate Gotabaya Rajapaksa in the 2019 presidential election.",
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa won the presidential election as expected by all parties. However, the entire political structure faced massive crises due to the wrong actions of the government.",
        "We fought from within the government to correct the mistakes, but no one paid any attention to our suggestions. The result was a political change that no one expected.",
        "Had I won the new presidential election in Parliament, I would have been considered the 8th president with executive powers. The presidential system with executive powers should be abolished completely. The executive presidential system is the main factor behind all the problems.",
        "People's voice and expectations are not respected in Parliament. People's expectations will change very soon. People's support for us and the People's Liberation Front is more than the strength of the Parliament, he said."
      ],
